*======================================================================
* SPICE Model generated by Coilcraft
* Coilcraft Part Number : XGL1712-103
* Inductance = 10uH
*======================================================================
* Model Parameters:
*   Valid Frequency Range = 0.0001GHz-0.05GHz
*   Ambient Temperature = 25 degC
*   DC Bias Current = 0 A
*   Non-Linear Frequency Dependent Approximation
*======================================================================
.subckt XGL1712-103 port1 port2 PARAMS: Cpar=37.8pF Ind=10uH
X1 port1 port2 Model1A PARAMS:
+ R1=4.2
+ R2=4.4E-03
+ C= {Cpar}
+ K1=0.000001
+ K2=1.02
+ K3= {Ind}
+ K4=1.00E-06
+ K5=1.00E-06
+ L=3.2409E-06
+ Is=10.0466074
+ a=0.67908918
+ L_Z0=0
+ L_EL=0
+ L_F0=0E6
.ends XGL1712-103

*======================================================================
* SPICE Model generated by Coilcraft
* Coilcraft Advanced Power Inductor Model
*======================================================================
* Model Parameters:
*   Valid Frequency Range Varies by Inductor
*   Ambient Temperature = 25 degC
*   DC Bias Current = 0 A
*   Non-Linear Frequency Dependent Model
*======================================================================
.subckt Model1A Lin Lout PARAMS:
+ R1=1
+ R2=1
+ C=1
+ K1=1
+ K2=1
+ K3=1
+ K4=1
+ K5=1
R2 N001 Lin {R2}
R1 Lout N002 {R1}
C1 N002 N001 {C}
G_Rvar2 N001 Lout LAPLACE { V(N001, Lout) } {1/K2/(-S*S/4/PI^2)^0.25}
G_Rvar1 N001 N003 LAPLACE { V(N001, N003) } {1/K1/(-S*S/4/PI^2)^0.25}
G_Lvar N003 Lout  LAPLACE { V(N003, Lout) } {1/(S*1e-6*({K3*1e6}-({K4}*LOG({K5}*(sqrt(-S*S)/(2*pi))))))}
*This large resistance to ground has been added to prevent a floating node error
R3 N003 0 100Meg
.ends Model1A

